# Spotify API Configuration
#
# Steps to get your Spotify Client ID:
# 1. Go to https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# 2. Log in with your Spotify account
# 3. Create a new app (name it "CD Collection to Playlist" or similar)
# 4. Copy the Client ID from your app settings
# 5. Add http://localhost:5173 to the "Redirect URIs" in your app settings
# 6. Save the settings in Spotify Dashboard
# 7. Paste your Client ID below
#
VITE_SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_spotify_client_id_here
VITE_SPOTIFY_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:5173
#
# Note: For production deployment, update VITE_SPOTIFY_REDIRECT_URI to your deployed URL
# Example: VITE_SPOTIFY_REDIRECT_URI=https://yourusername.github.io/CD-to-Spotify-PWA
